title: Swisstransplant Data Science
text:
Swisstransplant Data Science is an online portal by the Research and QM team to support core activities at Swisstransplant and the six transplant centers.
To learn more about Swisstransplant visit our website https://www.swisstransplant.org/.

title: About
text: The Data Science portal was created by Research and QM at Swisstransplant. To contact us visit our website at https://www.swisstransplant.org/.
